response.overview: Gail Kim is a world champion, Impact Hall of Famer and her legacy transcends the business. This is your chance to experience the matches and moments through her eyes. Join Gail, as she takes you on her wrestling journey in her own words. Greatest Matches Include: Victory Road 2006 Gail Kim & AMW vs. Styles, Daniels & Sirelda Bound For Glory 2007 Knockouts Gauntlet Turning Point 2007 Gail Kim vs. Awesome Kong Final Resolution 2008 Gail Kim vs Awesome Kong no dq. Destination X 2008 Gail Kim vs Awesome Kong vs ODB Victory Road 2008 Gail Kim vs Angelina Love IMPACT 8.21.2008 Gail Kim vs Kong street fight rules Genesis 2012 Gail Kim vs Mickie James Slammiversary 2013 Gail Kim vs Taryn Terrell Last KO Standing IMPACT 6.29.2013 Gail Kim vs Taryn Terrell Ladder Match IMPACT 6.23.2015 Gail Kim vs Jade Bound For Glory 2017 Gail Kim vs Allie vs Sienna Plus Many More!!
